Class JkPluginJava

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.tool.JkPlugin
      • dev.jeka.core.tool.builtins.java.JkPluginJava

  • public class JkPluginJava
extends JkPlugin
    Plugin for building Java projects. It comes with a JkJavaProject pre-configured with JkOptions. and a decoration for scaffolding.
